metadata.comment: Processes IRS zipcode data to filter out invalid zip codes, cast data types, and aggregate income brackets by zipcode. It calculates the percentage of high-income returns and flags zip codes with a high-income percentage above 10%. The pipeline then adds a sequence column to the data and joins it with customer data to produce a final dataset containing customer details along with their zip codes and income information.

condition.expression: zipcode != '00000' and zipcode != '99999' and zipcode is not null
